TI  - The Nonexistence of a Free Entry Cournot Equilibrium in Labor-Managed Economies
AU  - Laffont, J. J.
AU  - Moreaux, M.
AB  - [An example is given of a sequence of labor managed economies with decreasing efficiency sizes for which a free entry Cournot equilibrium fails to exist.]
